Package: picklerick
Title: Fast Single-Cell Format Conversion via SCX
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("SCX Authors", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "placeholder@example.com")
Description: R bindings to the SCX streaming interop engine for single-cell
    genomics. Converts between H5Seurat, H5AD, and SCX internal formats via
    a memory-bounded streaming pipeline. Returns 'anndataR::InMemoryAnnData'
    objects. No Python dependency.
License: GPL-3
Imports:
    anndataR (>= 0.0.1),
    Matrix
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
SystemRequirements: Cargo (rustup) >= 1.70
